    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The ratio of girls to boys is 1:5 at least in the BBI course",
          "name": "Daksh Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has more than 50+ clubs to be a part of and all the clubs are different which helps the students to learn more skills",
          "name": "Daksh Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is really nearby from Churchgate station, which makes it easier for the students who travel from far.",
          "name": "Khushi Rizwani",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "It's location exactly located 100-150m away from Marine lines heart of Mumbai.",
          "name": "Pranit",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is a lot of support in exams times, like notes, providing and doubts solving.",
          "name": "Khushi Rizwani",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "And students of hr college commerce from diverse backgrounds",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The food of canteen is so yum If yoh are spending most of the time in college due to fest practice the canteen food is the saviour and just like home",
          "name": "Sneha Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There's comfortness in every classroom. Each classroom has Ac's and touch screen boards for better understanding.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The celeb collaboration is very good they call such a high profiled celebs which inspires us and also give us great opportunities",
          "name": "Sneha Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "You can develop your leadership communication skills. As well as the sportsmanship personality.",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The attendance criteria of 75% is not maintained strictly in the college.",
          "name": "Khushi Rizwani",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The College does not have a appropriate campus area.",
          "name": "Khushi Rizwani",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college goes to online mode very frequently. This creates a lot of problem.",
          "name": "Manav Madia",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "AC doesn't work plus 24 hour network issue.",
          "name": "Moksha jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fees- The fees charged is exoberant, and is not ideal looking at the services provied,",
          "name": "Rishav Mohta",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The classroom being on the 5th floor and the students are not allowed to use the lifts, so we gotta climb 5floors each day",
          "name": "Daksh Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lectures are often called off quite a few times and because of this we gotta change our whole schedule",
          "name": "Daksh Jain",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are no strict rules in college, and they aim to help and pass all the students.",
          "name": "Khushi Rizwani",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The size of campus is too small and there is no ground.",
          "name": "Chitransh S Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
